	</div>



		<div id="box">
			    



        
	    	    



<div id="article-header">

                
	

    
        	    





		
										

        


                	    	
	



	    	    	    	    

	
	

 	
    
 	<div id="main-article-info">

		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline"
								>My life on a plate: famous foodies' food diaries</h1>
		
					<p itemprop="description" id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"                data-component="comp : r2 : Article : standfirst_cta"
			>Are Nigella's days spent scoffing chocolate cake? Does Heston blow-torch his dinner every night? And what&nbsp;does  the Guardian's restaurant critic eat when off-duty? We asked six foodies to share their week in meals, with illuminating results</p>
		
		
  	</div>

